Changed paths:
 M http://src.chromium.org/viewvc/native_client/trunk/src/native_client/SConstruct?r1=8146&amp;r2=8145&amp;pathrev=8146

Scons: Change PyAutoTester() to enforce dependencies

Pyauto expects to find all the files to serve in a single directory.
Rather than giving it the "staging" dir, copy all the files declared
as a dependency into a separate directory and run Pyauto on that.
This will help with catching undeclared dependencies.

This will also help with switching these tests to using generated NMF
files.

BUG=http://code.google.com/p/nativeclient/issues/detail?id=2645
TEST=pyauto_tests

